value: Resident and visitor, shallow saline water, also tidal flats when non-breeding: breeds N Somalia - South Africa on eastern side and to N Namibia away from coast; winters all around coasts.

Now breeds locally from Holland and the Island of Riigen (formerly from southern England and coasts of the Baltic Sea) eastward through the region of the Black and Caspian Seas, Kirghiz Steppes, the upper Yenessei and Transbaikalia, south to the Mediterranean countries, Persia, Turkes- tan and northern China; breeds also in various parts of tropical and south- ern Africa, possibly in Madagascar. Migrates from the northern part of its breeding range to Africa, India and southern China.
